---
title: Hoisin Pork Stir-Fry with Brown Rice, Sugar Snap Peas, and Ginger
description: We’re starting this stir-fry with an aromatic base of ginger, onion, and garlic. A touch of hoisin and lime gives the recipe the perfect balance of tangy, sweet, and salty. Hearty brown rice makes this dish a healthy spin on take-out.
